Interface PublicationEnricherListener

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface PublicationEnricherListener
extends EnricherListener<Publication>, PublicationChangeListener
    An extension of the PublicationChangeListener with specific methods related to the process of enriching. Each method will be fired after the change has been made to the publication.
    Since:
